\par\plain {\f2\fs36\b0\i0 Sample Documents}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 The \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Sample Output\u8221\'94 folder inside the Research folder contains examples of documents that have been created by compiling from this template. \u8220\'93Standard Manuscript\u8221\'94 shows the results when compiling to \u8220\'93Standard Manuscript Format (with Parts)\u8221\'94; \u8220\'93Paperback Novel\u8221\'94 shows the results when compiling to \u8220\'93Paperback Novel (with Parts)\u8221\'94 format; and \u8220\'93ADE E-Book\u8221\'94 shows the results when compiling to \u8220\'93E-book (with Parts)\u8221\'94 format and opening the resulting EPUB file in Adobe Digital Editions on a PC.}
